To my big surprise, right after our trip to Scotland, we find this beer we fell in love to from one of new local restaurants. Vanilla bomb!

Dark, burnt malts. A bit watery, more of an aftertaste than the first impression. You can definitely find the hops.

500ml bottle. Close to BBE date (28.8.2012). Nice malty taste, a bit watery. Light sweetness, nice bitter touch.
